// Wrong-patient safety proof — case data.
//
// This is a native, de-duplicated copy of the evidence generated by
// openadapt-flow's safety gallery
// (benchmark/safety_gallery/{results.json,gallery.html}). Every field here is
// the REAL recorded/live pair, the REAL OCR output, and the REAL verdict from
// the shipping identity check (verify_target_identity). No model, no network.
//
// Images in /public/safety/* are the actual rendered patient rows and
// magnified identifier crops decoded from that gallery — not mockups.
//
// Regenerate the source with:  python -m benchmark.safety_gallery.generate

